M|references|For layering realistic voiceovers onto video ads, adding narration to product demos, or generating audio for Remotion-rendered videos. These tools turn ad scripts into natural-sounding voice tracks.
M|references|Many video generators (Veo, Kling, Sora, Seedance) now include native audio. Use standalone voice tools when you need:
M|references|- **Voiceover on silent video** — Runway Gen-4 and Remotion produce silent output
M|references|- **Brand voice consistency** — Clone a specific voice for all ads
M|references|- **Multi-language versions** — Same ad script in 20+ languages
M|references|- **Script iteration** — Re-record voiceover without reshooting video
M|references|- **Precise control** — Exact timing, emotion, and pacing
M|references|The market leader in realistic voice generation and voice cloning.
M|references|**Best for:** Most natural-sounding voiceovers, brand voice cloning, multilingual
M|references|**API:** REST API with streaming support
M|references|**Pricing:** ~$0.12-0.30 per 1,000 characters depending on plan; starts at $5/month
M|references|**Capabilities:**
M|references|- 29+ languages with natural accent and intonation
M|references|- Voice cloning from short audio clips (instant) or longer recordings (professional)
M|references|- Emotion and style control
M|references|- Streaming for real-time generation
M|references|- Voice library with hundreds of pre-built voices
M|references|**Ad creative use cases:**
M|references|- gen voiceover tracks for video ads
M|references|- Clone your brand spokesperson's voice for all ad variations
M|references|- Produce the same ad in 10+ languages from one script
M|references|- A/B test different voice styles (authoritative vs. friendly vs. urgent)
M|references|**API example:**
M|references|```bash
M|references|curl -X POST "https://api.elevenlabs.io/v1/text-to-speech/{voice_id}" \
M|references|-H "xi-api-key: $ELEVENLABS_API_KEY" \
M|references|-H "cnt-Type: application/json" \
M|references|-d '{
M|references|"text": "Stop wasting hours on manual reporting. Try DataFlow free for 14 days.",
M|references|"model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
M|references|"voice_settings": {"stability": 0.5, "similarity_boost": 0.75}
M|references|}' --output voiceover.mp3
M|references|```
M|references|**Docs:** [ElevenLabs API](https://elevenlabs.io/docs/api-reference/text-to-speech)
M|references|Simple, affordable text-to-speech built into the OpenAI API.
M|references|**Best for:** Quick voiceovers, cost-effective at scale, simple integration
