M|references|**Pricing:** $15/million chars (standard), $30/million chars (HD); ~$0.015/min with gpt-4o-mini-tts
M|references|**Capabilities:**
M|references|- 13 built-in voices (no custom cloning)
M|references|- Multiple languages
M|references|- Real-time streaming
M|references|- HD quality option
M|references|- Simple API — same SDK you already use for GPT
M|references|**Ad creative use cases:**
M|references|- Fast, cheap voiceover for draft/test ad versions
M|references|- High-volume narration at low cost
M|references|- Prototype ad audio before investing in premium voice
M|references|**Docs:** [OpenAI TTS](https://platform.openai.com/docs/guides/text-to-speech)
M|references|Ultra-low latency voice generation built for real-time applications.
