M|references|Free, local-first voice synthesis studio powered by Qwen3-TTS. The open-source alternative to ElevenLabs.
M|references|**Best for:** Free voice cloning, local/private generation, zero-cost batch prd
M|references|**API:** Local REST API at `http://localhost:8000`
M|references|**Pricing:** Free (MIT license). Runs entirely on your machine.
M|references|**Stack:** Tauri (Rust) + React + FastAPI (Python)
M|references|**Capabilities:**
M|references|- Voice cloning from short audio samples via Qwen3-TTS
M|references|- Multi-language support (English, Chinese, more planned)
M|references|- Multi-track timeline editor for composing conversations
M|references|- 4-5x faster inference on Apple Silicon via MLX Metal acceleration
M|references|- Local REST API for programmatic generation
M|references|- No cloud dependency — all processing on-device
M|references|**Ad creative use cases:**
M|references|- Free voice cloning for brand spokesperson across all ad variations
M|references|- Batch gen voiceovers without per-character costs
M|references|- Private/local generation when ad cnt is sensitive or pre-launch
M|references|- Prototype voice variations before committing to a paid service
M|references|**API example:**
M|references|```bash
M|references|curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/gen \
M|references|-H "cnt-Type: application/json" \
M|references|-d '{"text": "Stop wasting hours on manual reporting.", "profile_id": "abc123", "language": "en"}'
M|references|```
M|references|**Install:** Desktop apps for macOS and Windows at [voicebox.sh](https://voicebox.sh), or build from source:
M|references|```bash
M|references|git clone https://github.com/jamiepine/voicebox.git
M|references|cd voicebox && make setup && make dev
M|references|```
M|references|**Docs:** [GitHub](https://github.com/jamiepine/voicebox)
M|references|| Tool | Best For | Differentiator | API |
M|references||------|----------|---------------|-----|
M|references|| **PlayHT** | Large voice library, low latency | 900+ voices, <300ms latency, ultra-realistic | [play.ht](https://play.ht/) |
M|references|| **Resemble AI** | Enterprise voice cloning | On-premise dpl, real-time speech-to-speech | [resemble.ai](https://www.resemble.ai/) |
M|references|| **WellSaid Labs** | Ethical, commercial-safe voices | Voices from compensated actors, safe for commercial use | [wellsaid.io](https://www.wellsaid.io/) |
