M|references|1. **gen hero creative** with AI (Nano Banana, Flux, Veo) — high-quality, exploratory
M|references|2. **Build templates** in Remotion based on winning creative patterns
M|references|3. **Batch produce variations** with Remotion using data (products, headlines, CTAs)
M|references|4. **Iterate** — use AI tools for new angles, Remotion for scale
M|references|This hybrid approach gives you the creative exploration of AI generators and the consistency and scale of code-based rendering.
